<div>   
<p> </p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">近几年来，一直在思考一个问题：教材中的内容都是昨天的科学，我们的目标是将学生送到明天的前沿。如何实现我们的目标？</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">传统教育注重知识的传授，注重教师讲，学生记。未来教育必须注重探索，只有具有探索精神和探索能力才可能到达</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">明天的前沿。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1.</span></span></strong><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">“表”与“里”</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是我们看待一切</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">事物</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的外表，</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是事物在我</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">们</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">心中产生的印象，</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">通俗地讲，</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"> </span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">就是我们见到的事物的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表面形象</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”是形成其“表”的原因。</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是事物的根本属性，通俗地讲，</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是事物更</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深层次的品质、规律。</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">我们认识</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">事物</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">总是从</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">事物的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">开始。</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">用眼睛看见的是</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">只有用心才能看见</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”，</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">即</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">浮于面，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”沉于心。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">2. 诗词</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">我们朗读的诗词是诗词的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”，</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">诗词的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是诗词的情感、意境和诗词的平、仄、韵、律。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">杜甫的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">七律</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“蜀相”：</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">丞相祠堂何处寻，锦官城外柏森森。</span>  <span style="font-family: 楷体;">映阶碧草自春色，隔叶黄鹂空好音。</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">三顾频烦天下计，两朝开济老臣心。</span>  <span style="font-family: 楷体;">出师未捷身先死，长使英雄泪满襟。</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="background: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">后人解析：</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">“蜀相”的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">前四句凭吊丞相祠堂，从景物描写中感怀现实，透露出诗人忧国忧民之心；后四句咏叹丞相才德。</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">“蜀相”，是</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1300</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年前的杜甫写</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1800</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年前的</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">诸葛亮，我们现代人去读</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“蜀相”</span></span><span style="color: #333333; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，也会深受</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">诗人</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">杜甫</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对祖国命运的许多期盼与憧憬的情感所感染</span></span><span style="color: #333333; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果不学习诗词很难学习诗词的平、仄、韵、律；如果不学习诗词不可能理解诗词的情感、意境。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">3. 物理学</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物理教材中的知识</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">(</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">定义、定理、公式等</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">)</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">仅仅是物理学的“表”，物理学的思维方式、研究方法等才是物理学的“里”。</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物理学的思维方式和研究方法比物理学的知识更重要。物理学的知识是物理学思维方式和研究方法的载体。学习物理学和学习诗词类似。如果不学习物理知识，很难领会物理学的思维方式和研究方法。如果不学习物理学的思维方式和研究方法，很难具有</span></span><span style="background: #FFFFFF; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">探索能力。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象与简化、建立理想模型等</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">——物理学中重要的思维方式和研究方法。实际问题很复杂，抽象与简化使物理学家透过现象抓住问题的本质，抓住的主要因素，去掉次要因素，将复杂的问题变为简单的、方便研究的问题。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">3.1 </span></span></strong><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象与简化</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实例</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1：</span></span></strong><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">摆</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物理学中单摆是个经过</span></span><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象和</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">简化的模型。它必须满足：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">① 摆角小于5°；② 摆线质量可忽略；③ 摆线柔软；④ 摆线不可伸长；⑤ 摆球质量固定不变；⑥ 摆球的直径要远小于摆线长度；⑦ 摆要处于无阻尼环境；⑧ 摆要处于惯性系中等8个理想化条件。经过这些</span></span><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">简化，才能出现既好研究又具有代表性的单摆。如果不经简化，则有</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">8个变量，经过组合</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">      </span><img width="332" height="26" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">即有</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">256个问题，单摆只是其中的一个问题。余下255个问题中，有的问题是可研究的，有些问题困难到当前还无法研究。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br></span></span></p><p><a href="http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202206/16/160217rsbkl5jku0jle7kd.png" target="_blank"><img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202206/16/160217rsbkl5jku0jle7kd.png.thumb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><br></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（引用南京大学卢德馨教授的课件）</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">3.2 </span></span></strong><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象与简化</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">实例</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">2：</span></span></strong><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">分子平均碰撞次数和平均自由程</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">自由程：分子两次相邻碰撞之间自由通过的路程。分子平均自由程：每两次连续碰撞之间，一个分子自由运动的平均路程。分子平均碰撞次数：单位时间内一个分子和其它分子碰撞的平均次数。在标准状态下气体分子为</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">10</span></span><sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: super;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19</span></span></sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">/cm</span></span><sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: super;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">3</span></span></sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，研究起来看似相当困难。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br></span></span></p><p><a href="http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202206/16/160222jdb6mw8aummvxxbr.png" target="_blank"><img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202206/16/160222jdb6mw8aummvxxbr.png.thumb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br></span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br></span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">经过抽象与简化</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的模型。它必须满足：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">(1)</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">理想气体；</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">(2)将分子视为直径为d的弹性小球；(3)分子</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">α</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的平均速率为</span></span><img width="15" height="16" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，其他分子静止；</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">(4) 分子间的碰撞是完全弹性碰撞。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">如果以</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1s内分子</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">α</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的球心所经过的轨迹为轴，以</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">d为半径作一圆柱体，由于圆柱体的长度为</span></span><img width="15" height="16" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，所以圆柱体的体积是</span></span><img width="39" height="23" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，球心在这圆柱体内的其他分子，均将与分子</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family:;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">α</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">发生碰撞。设分子数密度为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">n，则圆柱体内分子的平均碰撞频率</span></span><img width="18" height="20" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为</span></span><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span></span></strong><img width="83" height="23" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。平均自由程</span></span><img width="15" height="23" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为：</span></span><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></strong><img width="100" height="44" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">考虑其它分子的运动等因素，修正后：</span></span><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">   </span></strong><img width="88" height="44" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">各种气体分子都以每秒钟数百米的速度无规则的热运动。平均碰撞频率</span></span><img width="16" height="20" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的数量级为</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">10</span></span><sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: super;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">9</span></span></sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">/s</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，也就是说。平均自由程</span></span><img width="18" height="22" src="data:image/png;base64," referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的数量级为</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">10</span></span><sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: super;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">-8</span></span></sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">m~10</span></span><sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: super;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">-7</span></span></sup><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">m</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">左右。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="color: #000000; line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">抽象与简化的实例在物理学中有很多，俯首可得，但是我们对其关注不够。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">3. </span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">总结</span></span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“表”</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">只能</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“形”似，学</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“里”才能“神”似。仅</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学习知识，永远只能跟在别人的后面；学会探索才可能到达前沿。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">不学习诗词的平、仄、韵、律，只能写出</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“顺口流儿”；写的东西缺少情感、意境，只能是白纸被墨迹所污。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学过物理学后，面对</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">自己研究领域中复杂的实际问题，</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">不会用</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物理学的思维方式、研究方法，将</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">复杂的实际问题通过抽象与简化建立起简单的、方便研究的模型，不能解决自己研究领域中的问题</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">只能说，仅</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">学了</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物理学的毛皮。只能成为一个普通的工作者，没有能力到达前沿。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 1em 0px 8px; line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1936 年 10 月 15 日，爱因斯坦在纽约州立大学第 72 届毕业典礼上的发言中讲，</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">被放在首要位置的永远应该是独立思考和判断的总体能力的培养，而不是获取特定的知识。如果一个人掌握了他的学科的基本原理，并学会了如何独立地思考和工作，他肯定会找到属于他的道路。除此之外，与那些接受的训练主要只包括获取详细知识的人相比，他更加能够使自己适应进步和变化</span></span><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 130%; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="line-height: 130%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">真诚的欢迎您的批评，借用您的智慧完善我的思想。</span></span></p><p></p>                    <br><br>
